Text Query: How many stars are in milky way galaxy?
Generated SQL Query: SELECT COUNT(performance_id::TEXT::INT) AS star_count FROM analytics.product_performance WHERE product_name ilike '%milky%way%galaxy%'

Text Query: Show me the names of employees and their departments.
Generated SQL Query: SELECT e.first_name, e.last_name, d.department_name FROM sales.employees AS e JOIN sales.departments AS d ON e.department_id = d.department_id;
